import {Container, HeaderChess, Alpha} from '../style/style'
import Image from 'next/image'


function Home () {
    return (
        <Alpha>
            <Container >
                <HeaderChess>
                    <Image src="/chess.webp" quality="100" responsive="true" width="1600" height="700"/>
                </HeaderChess>
            </Container>
        </Alpha>
        
    )
}

export default Home
